Once upon a time, there was a weasel who had the ability to hypnotise snails. This was an amazing talent and the weasel was quite proud of it. He would often take his flock into the meadow and hypnotise the snails that lived there. The snails would become mesmerised and follow the weasel around, while the other weasel watched in amazement.

The weasel was so good at hypnotising snails that he eventually decided to make a living out of it. He would go to different towns, perform his shows and charge people for the entertainment. People would come from far and wide to see the weasel perform his mesmerising trick.

The weasel was very popular and even famous in some circles. He would often be invited to perform at parties and events, where he would mesmerise the snails even further. The snails would follow him around like little puppies, and people would be fascinated by this strange and wonderful talent.

